  "texts": [
    "Take your time to think about this question, and I'm here to assist you!",
    "According to my understanding, some schools offer special courses, such as taking students to visit science and technology museums, and then organizing science and technology workshops to let students design some productions.",
    "In this process, students can improve their hands-on skills, teamwork skills, communication skills, etc.",
    "At the same time, I think it is very important that in such activities, students can feel the sense of achievement in learning, which is very helpful for them to realize that learning itself is a happy and interesting thing, so it is conducive to improving their interest in learning and establish their concept of lifelong learning.",
    "That's an excellent observation, Tony!"
  ]
}